                                "byte_start": 86614,
                                "byte_stop": 134679,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court in No. 87-7028, and a companion case in Mistretta against the United States will be announced by Justice Blackmun."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 12.002,
                        "stop": 126.746,
